      "title": "Lawyers in Aluthkade Satyagraha",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A symbolic satyagraha organized by the Bar Community will be held today (01) in front of the Hulftsdorp Courts Complex.",
        "They are engaged in a satyagraha demanding the resignation of the oppressive government.",
        "It was attended by a large number of lawyers and he protested by sitting on the pavement in front of the court complex and displaying various placards."
      ],
